projects.name: Docter-Appointment
projects.description: Developed a Doctor Appointment application utilizing HTML, CSS, JavaScript, PHP, and MySQL. Integrated a user authentication system, including login and signup pages, using HTML, CSS, JavaScript, and MySQL for data storage. Designed and implemented a comprehensive dashboard with features such as scheduling appointments and accessing patient details.

projects.name: Movie Clone with Api
projects.description: Developed a Movie API application utilizing React.js, HTML, CSS, JavaScript, and REST API. Created a user-friendly interface for managing movie data, including features for browsing and searching. Implemented functionality to fetch the latest movie data and organize it within the applications home page. Managed database operations and integrated new modules with existing ones to ensure seamless functionality.

projects.name: Bus PMPL Pune
projects.description: Developed a scalable and performant bus ticketing application using React.js, Tailwind CSS, and JavaScript. Implemented validation for the login page and enhanced the user interface of the home page. Integrated QR code authentication and Stripe for secure payment processing. Significantly reduced server processing load by 50% through efficient QR code scanning implementation and optimization.

projects.name: Crime Predication with machine Learning
projects.description: Developed a crime prediction system using machine learning techniques in Python. Utilized libraries such as NumPy, Pandas, and Matplotlib for data processing and visualization. Implemented predictive models to forecast crime occurrences based on historical data. Enhanced the accuracy and performance of the prediction system through iterative testing and optimization.
